messages.message:
Hi Subash
Which branch is this on ?
I am seeing dogfood deploy today morning worked fine and its green in DM too.
https://dogfood.instabase.com/deployment-manager/dashboard/deployments/apps/v1/webapp
It is on master branch. Even aihub-sandbox deployments are green. I wonder If I am missing something

since the error seems to come from a unit test, is this happening when you run unit tests or when you try to build the `webapp` docker container?

also, do you need local `webapp` changes to be included? if not, i usually do `ppy compile webapp --as-docker --use-prebuilt` to get the `webapp` docker container built in our Jenkins CD pipelines
